text:
Browse > Home / Local News / Prepare for lane closure on Northeast High Street Prepare for lane closure on Northeast High Street 
October 20, 2015 
NEW — 3:45 p.m. Oct. 20, 2015 
Drivers should prepare for a lane closure on Northeast High Street Oct 21-22. 
The city will close westbound lane between Ninth Avenue Northeast and Highlands Drive Northeast daily from 9 a.m. to 2:30 p.m. 
The closure is needed as equipment is installed on top of a building along High Street.
